    <title>Maven国内镜像加速</title>
    <link href="/2023/09/02/Maven%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F/"/>
    <url>/2023/09/02/Maven%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Maven是什么"><a href="#Maven是什么" class="headerlink" title="Maven是什么"></a>Maven是什么</h2><p>Apache Maven是目前主流的项目管理工具，但国内使用Maven下载软件时会非常慢，因为是从官方源下载。<br>这时候就需要使用Maven的国内镜像源，下面提供国内三个比较主流的镜像源：</p><ul><li>阿里云 <a href="https://developer.aliyun.com/mvn/guide">https://developer.aliyun.com/mvn/guide</a></li><li>腾讯云 <a href="https://mirrors.cloud.tencent.com/">https://mirrors.cloud.tencent.com/</a></li><li>华为云 <a href="https://mirrors.huaweicloud.com/">https://mirrors.huaweicloud.com/</a></li></ul><h2 id="如何获取Maven镜像源"><a href="#如何获取Maven镜像源" class="headerlink" title="如何获取Maven镜像源"></a>如何获取Maven镜像源</h2><h3 id="阿里云："><a href="#阿里云：" class="headerlink" title="阿里云："></a>阿里云：</h3><p>打开阿里云的网址，点击<code>maven 配置指南</code>,在右侧栏就能看到阿里云的镜像源信息：</p><img src="/2023/09/02/Maven%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F/aliyun_maven.png" class="" title="阿里云Maven镜像源"><h3 id="腾讯云："><a href="#腾讯云：" class="headerlink" title="腾讯云："></a>腾讯云：</h3><p>打开腾讯云的网址，用快捷键<code>CTRL+F</code>网页搜索<code>Maven</code>，找到Maven，点击右边的”查看”按钮，就能看到腾讯云的镜像源信息：</p><img src="/2023/09/02/Maven%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F/Tencent_maven1.png" class="" title="腾讯云Maven镜像源"><img src="/2023/09/02/Maven%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F/Tencent_maven2.png" class="" title="腾讯云Maven镜像源"><h3 id="华为云："><a href="#华为云：" class="headerlink" title="华为云："></a>华为云：</h3><p>打开华为云的网址，在搜索栏输入<code>Maven</code>，在搜索结果里点击<code>Maven</code>，就能看到华为云的镜像源信息：</p><img src="/2023/09/02/Maven%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F/huawei_maven.png" class="" title="华为云Maven镜像源"><img src="/2023/09/02/Maven%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F/huawei_maven1.png" class="" title="华为云Maven镜像源"><h2 id="IDEA如何配置Maven镜像源"><a href="#IDEA如何配置Maven镜像源" class="headerlink" title="IDEA如何配置Maven镜像源"></a>IDEA如何配置Maven镜像源</h2><p>打开IDEA的设置，File -&gt; Settings，搜索Maven的设置信息：</p><img src="/2023/09/02/Maven%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F/idea_maven_setting.png" class=""><figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crmsh">Maven home directory: Maven插件的根目录<br><span class="hljs-keyword">User</span> <span class="hljs-title">setting</span> file: Maven的设置文件，把镜像源放在setting.xml里面<br>Local repository: Maven下载的jar包目录，可以改到D盘或E盘<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/2023/09/02/Maven%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F/idea_maven1.png" class=""><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">mirror</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">id</span>&gt;</span>aliyunmaven<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">id</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">mirrorOf</span>&gt;</span>*<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">mirrorOf</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span>阿里云公共仓库<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">url</span>&gt;</span>https://maven.aliyun.com/repository/public<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">url</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">mirror</span>&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">mirror</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">id</span>&gt;</span>nexus-tencentyun<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">id</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">mirrorOf</span>&gt;</span>*<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">mirrorOf</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span>Nexus tencentyun<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">name</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">url</span>&gt;</span>http://mirrors.cloud.tencent.com/nexus/repository/maven-public/<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">url</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">mirror</span>&gt;</span> <br><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">mirror</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">id</span>&gt;</span>huaweicloud<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">id</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">mirrorOf</span>&gt;</span>*<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">mirrorOf</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">url</span>&gt;</span>https://repo.huaweicloud.com/repository/maven/<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">url</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">mirror</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
